avengers grimm is a 2015 american fantasy action adventure film written , co-edited , and directed by jeremy m. inman .   the film , produced by b-movie film company the asylum , stars casper van dien , lou ferrigno , kimo leopoldo , lauren parkinson , milynn sarley , marah fairclough , rileah vanderbilt , and elizabeth peterson .   the film is a mockbuster of the marvel studios superhero film avengers : age of ultron and the abc tv series once upon a time .